新的任天堂3DS及其XL型号最早于2014年11月21日在日本以外的澳大利亚和新西兰发布，但较小的型号只有白色供选择。<ref name="New N3DS at Polygon">{{cite web |title=Nintendo reveals the New Nintendo 3DS |first=Emily |last=Gera |date=August 29, 2014 |url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/8/29/6082241/nintendo-reveals-the-new-nintendo-3ds |publisher=Polygon |accessdate=August 29, 2014 |archive-date=2018-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180629074224/https://www.polygon.com/2014/8/29/6082241/nintendo-reveals-the-new-nintendo-3ds |dead-url=no }}</ref> 在欧洲，新任天堂3DS于2015年1月6日首次在线上网站提供，其中包含一个特殊的白色“大使版”套装，专用于{{tsl|en|Club_Nintendo|任天堂俱乐部}}会员，并配有充电底座和两个替换面板。<ref name=engadget-new3dseurope>{{cite web|title=New Nintendo 3DS comes to Europe as Ambassador Edition|url=https://www.engadget.com/2015/01/06/nintendo-3ds-ambassador-edition/|website=Engadget|accessdate=January 14, 2015|archive-date=2018-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180523172650/https://www.engadget.com/2015/01/06/nintendo-3ds-ambassador-edition/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年1月14日，任天堂宣布，新系统将于2015年2月13日在北美和欧洲的零售店发售。在欧洲，新任天堂3DS有黑色或白色可供选择，其XL型号拥有金属黑或金属蓝可供选择。在北美，XL型号发布了金属红和金属黑（后更名为“新红”和“新黑”）。而特别限量机型《[[薩爾達傳說_穆修拉的假面|薩爾達傳說 穆修拉的假面]]》和《[[怪物猎人4|怪物猎人4]]》也在两个地区发布<ref name=polygon-usrelease>{{cite web|title=New Nintendo 3DS XL hits North America Feb. 13|url=http://www.polygon.com/2015/1/14/7540289/new-nintendo-3ds|website=Polygon|accessdate=January 14, 2015|archive-date=2019-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129064112/https://www.polygon.com/2015/1/14/7540289/new-nintendo-3ds|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=eurna-release-gamespot>{{cite web|title=New Nintendo 3DS Release Date Confirmed—Only XL Version Coming to US|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/new-nintendo-3ds-release-date-confirmed-only-xl-ve/1100-6424634/|website=GameSpot|publisher=CBS Interactive|accessdate=January 14, 2015|archive-date=2019-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129064247/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/new-nintendo-3ds-release-date-confirmed-only-xl-ve/1100-6424634/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=gamesradar-new3dseurope>{{cite web|title=New 3DS coming on February 13, no smaller version for North America|url=http://www.gamesradar.com/new-3ds-review/|website=GamesRadar|accessdate=January 14, 2015|archive-date=2018-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180524003655/https://www.gamesradar.com/new-3ds-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。在欧洲和北美第一周的供货期间共销售了335,000台。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Phillips|first1=Tom|title=New Nintendo 3DS sold 335k during EU/US launch week|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-02-17-new-nintendo-3ds-sold-335k-during-eu-us-launch-week|website=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|publisher=Gamer Network|accessdate=February 17, 2015|date=February 17, 2015|archive-date=2018-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180524004124/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-02-17-new-nintendo-3ds-sold-335k-during-eu-us-launch-week|dead-url=no}}</ref>

最初只有XL模型在北美发布的;尽管任天堂不排除将来会发布普通新任天堂3DS的可能性，但任天堂美国代表达蒙贝克解释说，他们不想混淆消费者，而且替换面板供货量不足以满足销售的小型机型<ref name=gamespot-no3dsna>{{cite web|title=Nintendo Explains Why Smaller New 3DS Isn't Coming to US|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/nintendo-explains-why-smaller-new-3ds-isn-t-coming/1100-6424665/|website=GameSpot|publisher=CBS Interactive|date=January 15, 2015|accessdate=January 17, 2015|archive-date=2017-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015044232/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/nintendo-explains-why-smaller-new-3ds-isn-t-coming/1100-6424665/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Makuch|first1=Eddie|title=Nintendo Rep Explains Why Smaller New Nintendo 3DS Wasn't Released in US|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/nintendo-rep-explains-why-smaller-new-nintendo-3ds/1100-6425373/|website=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|accessdate=February 19, 2015|archive-date=2017-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171014234500/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/nintendo-rep-explains-why-smaller-new-nintendo-3ds/1100-6425373/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。出现了一个[[社交媒体|社交媒体]]运动，呼吁任天堂美国公司在北美发布该小型机型<ref>{{cite web|first=Jason|last=Schreier|url=http://kotaku.com/people-really-want-the-smaller-new-3ds-1680450443|title=People ''Really'' Want The Smaller New 3DS|publisher=Kotaku|date=January 19, 2015|accessdate=June 4, 2015|archive-date=2017-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015044312/https://kotaku.com/people-really-want-the-smaller-new-3ds-1680450443|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 2015年3月，[[FCC|美国联邦通信委员会]]解除了有关2014年9月在标准新任天堂3DS机型上执行的监管细节的信息禁令，这表明任天堂美国确实考虑在一个时间点推出小型机型<ref name="NLcitesFCCdetailsstandardNN3DS">{{cite web |first=Conor |last=McMahon |url=http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2015/03/standard-sized_new_nintendo_3ds_photos_emerge_on_fcc_website_in_north_america |title=Standard-Sized New Nintendo 3DS Photos Emerge On FCC Website in North America |publisher=Nintendo Life |date=March 24, 2015 |accessdate=May 6, 2015 |archive-date=2018-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180904131242/http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2015/03/standard-sized_new_nintendo_3ds_photos_emerge_on_fcc_website_in_north_america |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

